Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.50,Insert - CN - 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(1830,30)\alpha&H00&}在海天一色的静谧里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:20.35,Insert - CN - 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(1830,30)\alpha&H00&}尽管知晓只有我们彼此
